{"tid":2086680,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[不散] 民間集會團隊將堅守戰線 繼續入紙","createTime":"2020-06-30T11:15:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T14:14:37.000Z","uid":42194,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"926d61482b6ef74bbb5728d8296f43ba1a32cd07","tid":2086680,"uid":42194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:15:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/unwF0v4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FunwF0v4.png&h=36186937&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n民間集會團隊將堅守戰線，繼續入紙。<br />\n<br />\n面對一紙未知內容的国安惡法，民間集會團隊(下稱民集) 全體入紙師仝人將堅守戰線，繼續入紙，誓與手足齊上齊落。<br />\n<br />\n而早前已改期於7月3日舉行之抗爭一週年集會將因限聚令再三延長而再次改期，並訂於7月17日，即限聚令完結的第一天舉行。<br />\n<br />\n最後，明天為7月1日，民集懇請香港人加油，萬事小心。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n<br />\n民間集會團隊<br />\n2020年6月30日"},{"pid":"8a665cb9aaf7eb4c49352ab5fa952554a401e2dd","tid":2086680,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:16:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34184e052b7bac65c8f995c72b9569ec46661915","tid":2086680,"uid":333752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:17:29.000Z","msg":"7.1 維園見，努力airdrop，唔好再圍爐！"},{"pid":"49766416dc5f3708efc7c6dc6ea5a886884ca9d9","tid":2086680,"uid":42194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:17:55.000Z","msg":"民集懇請大家再次欣賞以想下片段，重燃鬥志。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/83j2GRJEmEk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F83j2GRJEmEk&d=r9GgQvVcrWtMp%2Fshn5VX%2Fwy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=81292684\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/83j2GRJEmEk</a>"},{"pid":"2d8059f6d4717f2ec2a92d1d1b235b62187c48eb","tid":2086680,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:18:54.000Z","msg":"都係個句, 